  <h1 style="text-align:center; color:#8B4513; font-family:Georgia;">Khaana: An American Bar & Grill</h1>
  <h2 style="text-align:center; color:#D2691E;">Our Story and History</h2>
  
  <div style="text-align:center; margin:20px 0;">
    <img src="Burger.jpg" alt="Khaana Signature Burger" style="max-width:100%; border-radius:8px;">
  </div>
  
  <p><b>Khaana</b> was founded in <u>1999</u> as a <i>bar and grill</i> in <b>West Lafayette, Indiana</b>. 
  Our mission is to serve homestyle American food, refreshing drinks, and create a 
  <span style="color:red;"><b>community</b></span> gathering place for all. Over time, we grew into a 
  <span style="font-size:22px;">local favorite</span> known for hearty meals and community spirit.</p>
  
  <p style="color:#2F4F2F;">What started as a small neighborhood bar has blossomed into a beloved 
  West Lafayette institution. Our founders believed great food could transform strangers into friends. 
  That belief guides everything we do today.</p>
  
  <h2 style="text-align:center; color:#D2691E;">Khaana History Timeline</h2>
  <ol>
    <li>1999 – First location opens in West Lafayette</li>
    <li>2005 – Added a second location</li>
    <li>2006 – Extended hours until midnight and added premium craft beers</li>
    <li>2015 – Recognized on Yelp as a Top Bar & Grill</li>
    <li>2020 – Adapted to serve our community with takeout and delivery with DoorDash</li>
  </ol>
  
  <h2 style="text-align:center; color:#D2691E;">Our Core Values</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Customers are always our number one priority</li>
    <li>Classic American comfort food made with fresh ingredients</li>
    <li>Supporting our local West Lafayette community</li>
    <li>Guaranteed tasty or your meal is on us!</li>
  </ul>
  
